#!
# premade query answers

$ORIGIN example.com.
$TTL 3600

# reply AXFR request
ENTRY_BEGIN
MATCH opcode qtype qname
REPLY QR NOERROR
ADJUST copy_id
SECTION QUESTION
@ IN AXFR
SECTION ANSWER
@ 345600 IN SOA ns0.example.org. root 3 3600 28800 2419200 3600
; 0001(family) prefix afdlength 0x40, 64xaa
x APL \# 68 0001 18 40 aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa
@ 345600 IN SOA ns0.example.org. root 3 3600 28800 2419200 3600
ENTRY_END
